Plot:

Lord of Asses 11 by director Tom Byron for Tom Byron Pictures was an extremely solid movie and I rated it as Highly Recommended based on the performances of Delilah Strong, Annette Schwarz, August, and of course, Brianna Love but Tatiana showed some nice potential too. The technical matters were a bit better than the last volume I reviewed and the heat generated was really appreciated, proving that Tom has a lot of staying power compared to many pretenders to his throne. In short, Lord of Asses 11 raised the bar enough that I openly wonder if Tom will be able to outdo himself next time or if he'll have to retire the series, knowing full well that the former Houstonian still has a few tricks up his sleeve so I'll be on the look out
